---
title: Smart Caramelized Onion Chicken with Garlic Zucchini and Peppers
description: This special-occasion dinner is a magical medley of gourmet flavours, including succulent chicken and caramelized onions. Set the table and pour the wine while these flavours mingle together to create a meal that's nothing short of memorable!

